162
00:31:57,999 --> 00:31:58,958
Your personality.

163
00:32:00,501 --> 00:32:01,878
You act like a dork.

164
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:04,631
I see.

165
00:32:05,089 --> 00:32:06,591
