188
00:34:04,834 --> 00:34:05,835
Crying?

189
00:34:05,918 --> 00:34:07,003
Oh, please.

190
00:34:11,382 --> 00:34:12,341
Take this.

191
00:34:12,884 --> 00:34:13,926
